		"name": "Airline Booking System - Microservices (Detailed)",
		"description": "A comprehensive Postman collection to test and assert the Airline Booking System microservices including Eureka Server, Flight Service, Seat Service, Payment Service, and Ticket Service. Every request contains automated tests to check status codes and response bodies.",
